  "body": "1) Colors\n\n* [ ] [GHI xs] rename colors names according to figma \nExample: `Light Grey` -> `:light-grey`\nFigma: https://www.figma.com/file/cb4p8AxLtTF3q1L6JYDnKN15/Index?node-id=787%3A807\n\n2) Icons\n\n* [ ] [GHI xs] rename namespace `status-im.ui.components.icons.vector-icons` to `status-im.ui.components.icons` and `vector-icons` aliases to `icons`\n\n3) List items\n\n* [ ] [GHI m] replace all implementation and usages in the app by `list-item` component, remove item components in `status-im.ui.components.list.views`, move `status-im.ui.components.list.views to status-im.ui.components.react`\n\n4) Top bar\n\n* [ ] https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/8981 implement topbar component similar to list-item component, move statusbar into topbar, replace all usages of statusbar and toolbar on new topbar, implement `{:type :big}` for topbar and use large-toolbar implementation\nFirst iteration https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/9711\n\n5) UI elements (buttons , switches, checkboxes) \n\n* [ ] [GHI s] replace all implementation and usages in the app by new UI elements \n\n6) Toolbar \n\n* [ ] [GHI s] replace all implementation and usages in the app by new toolbar\n\n7) Snackbar \n\n* [ ] [GHI s] implement snackbar similar to list-item",
